I like this change a lot I think it makes it more clear to reason about the name, certainly.
Now I'm going to propose a change that will touch every line of the PR just about, but is also a simple rename refactor in Android Studio :-), "Splitted" is not a valid word in English, and the variable really represents an array of the variable's components, so perhaps:




